Package: bpartysdazaa
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Simulating Ice Cream Party Resources
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sofia Daza
Maintainer:Sofia Daza <sofia.dazaarandia@unil.ch>
Description: A package designed to assist in the planning and simulation, 
    of resources for an ice cream party. The package 
    includes functions for calculating cone dimensions, simulating 
    weather-based guest attendance, and estimating the amount of ice cream required 
    to meet demand under various scenarios. It retrieves weather forecasts from the 
    OpenWeather API to incorporate climatic factors into resource planning.
